briefdescription.para: Deinitializes the BKP peripheral registers to their default reset values.
Configures the Tamper Pin active level.

parameterdescription.para:
specifies the Tamper Pin active level. This parameter can be one of the following values:
BKP_TamperPinLevel_High: Tamper pin active on high level
BKP_TamperPinLevel_Low: Tamper pin active on low level

briefdescription.para: Enables or disables the Tamper Pin activation.

parameterdescription.para: new state of the Tamper Pin activation. This parameter can be: ENABLE or DISABLE.

briefdescription.para: Enables or disables the Tamper Pin Interrupt.

parameterdescription.para: new state of the Tamper Pin Interrupt. This parameter can be: ENABLE or DISABLE.

briefdescription.para: Select the RTC output source to output on the Tamper pin.

parameterdescription.para:
specifies the RTC output source. This parameter can be one of the following values:
BKP_RTCOutputSource_None: no RTC output on the Tamper pin.
BKP_RTCOutputSource_CalibClock: output the RTC clock with frequency divided by 64 on the Tamper pin.
BKP_RTCOutputSource_Alarm: output the RTC Alarm pulse signal on the Tamper pin.
BKP_RTCOutputSource_Second: output the RTC Second pulse signal on the Tamper pin.
specifies the RTC Clock Calibration value. This parameter must be a number between 0 and 0x7F.

briefdescription.para: Writes user data to the specified Data Backup Register.

parameterdescription.para: specifies the Data Backup Register. This parameter can be BKP_DRx where x:[1, 42]

briefdescription.para: Reads data from the specified Data Backup Register.

parameterdescription.para: specifies the Data Backup Register. This parameter can be BKP_DRx where x:[1, 42]
content of the specified Data Backup Register

briefdescription.para: Checks whether the Tamper Pin Event flag is set or not.

parameterdescription.para: new state of the Tamper Pin Event flag (SET or RESET).

briefdescription.para: Clears Tamper Pin Event pending flag.
Checks whether the Tamper Pin Interrupt has occurred or not.

parameterdescription.para: new state of the Tamper Pin Interrupt (SET or RESET).

briefdescription.para: Clears Tamper Pin Interrupt pending bit.
